{"tid":1046704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"八達通擴支付途徑　月內推虛擬預付卡供網上消費","createTime":"2019-03-04T12:23:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T13:14:31.000Z","uid":27047,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e7ef51cc5878e1fe0f7bab3ae605fe6d8973faf0","tid":1046704,"uid":27047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T12:23:58.000Z","msg":"電子支付發展愈來愈蓬勃。八達通公司表示，將於本月與Mastercard(萬事達卡)合作推出虛擬預付卡，供用戶作網上消費，但該預付卡初期不能綁定除O！ePay外的電子錢包。另外，今年1月份的公共交通費用補貼金額逾80%已被領取，逾7成人已領取補貼。 <br />\n<br />\n八達通公司今日(4日)舉行傳媒春茗，該公司行政總裁張耀堂表示，本月內推出的虛擬預付方式將進一步拓展八達通的網上支付途徑。據悉，該預付卡與八達通電子錢包O！ePay綁定，預付卡的面額與電子錢包的餘額相同，上限1萬港元，<span style=\"color: red;\">可用作網上消費，例如在Google Play或蘋果App Store上消費，但初期不能綁定Apple Pay等電子錢包。 </span><br />\n<br />\n另外，八達通去年再戰的士市場，現時約有5000名的士司機參與以商業版O！ePay收取車資，總佔全港的士司機總數約八分之一。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190304/mobile/bkn-20190304150339649-0304_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190304%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190304150339649-0304_00822_001.html&d=i31y%2FnPqUiKwTWzPt1MI4DIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=e885ccf2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190304/mobile/bkn-20190304150339649-0304_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即係冇撚用"},{"pid":"f65647126cbddd939c2c2b1e5fd039d220710a78","tid":1046704,"uid":29021,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T12:25:00.000Z","msg":"竹你老母"},{"pid":"0bd6c01232e9a6b9a14e69c3b63c70f3fa3ace65","tid":1046704,"uid":29021,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f65647126cbddd939c2c2b1e5fd039d220710a78","tid":1046704,"uid":29021,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T12:25:00.000Z","msg":"竹你老母"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T12:25:11.000Z","msg":"sorry 錯頻"},{"pid":"800ed8e6a4400d37c0f87b736447f0b3bf60ddbf","tid":1046704,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"re